text:
Open Concept Food Court with wide range of food selection.
Is a good night dining experience.
Dining Crowd in Saturday Night is encouraging.
Q time for the food relatively longer for several stall like Roasted, Fish Soup, ZeCha…
Variety of Mixed Rice is very wide.
Carpark is right behind Block 622 so access via Car is good too.
The staff is rude… average food. Not very hygiene

A female coffee assistant in a coffee shop is so unqualified. She shines a laser light on a customer like a dog, which is really rude. Then she doesn’t apologize, and there is no complaint phone number to report the situation. I’m really angry.
